	<h1 class="title">这个叫“唐人街美人”的摄影项目，你猜拍的是谁？｜好奇心人类学</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/75588/small/75588.jpg?1431919455" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">张金晶 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-14 15:46:17 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/20718/medium/20718.jpg?1452753520" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="20718" data-title="《这个叫“唐人街美人”的摄影项目，你猜拍的是谁？｜好奇心人类学》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/20718/medium/20718.jpg?1452753520" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/20718.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
